=80=94 and Apple should not be compelled to put backdoors into iPhones =E2=
=80=94 but it's ok if the most convenient cloud complements to a user's dev=
ices are not end-to-end encrypted; that's a compromise position that gives =
each faction a bit of what they want, if not everything.

